"Zer-Li" - Group 6

Packages 
Package Description
ClientSide
'Client' project contains all the functionality of the client side.
ClientSide.boundaries
'boundaries' package contains all the UI files.
ClientSide.boundaries.images
'boundaries.images' package contains the images which used by the classes in 'boundaries' package.
ClientSide.client
'client' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.
ClientSide.controllers
'controllers' package contains the classes which has the UI logic.
CommonLib
'Common' is not a runnable project contains interfaces and classes which are shared both to the server and to the client.
CommonLib.common
'common' package contains interfaces and classes that do not stand alone and can be used in any project.
CommonLib.common.images
'common.images' package contains the images which used by the classes in 'common' package.
CommonLib.entities
'entities' package contains all the entities that related to the client and the server.
CommonLib.logger
'logger' package contains an singleton implementation to logger, which log to the console and to external file.
CommonLib.messages
'message' package contains all the messages mechanism of the communication between the client and the server.
CommonLib.utilities
'utilities' package contains static methods with some specific utilities.
ServerSide
'Server' project contains all the functionality of the server side.
ServerSide.configurations
'configurations' package contains all the configurations that related to the 'server' and has classes that can create and treat them.
ServerSide.connectivity
'connectivity' package contains the classes that related to server configuration.
ServerSide.db
'db' package contains the classes that responsible on the communication with the database.
ServerSide.server
'server' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.
